  "title": "FAPO Turbo for 07-12 Acura RDX K23A1 2.3L 2300DO-VT.T Mitsubishi TD04HL 49389",
  "handle": "fapo-turbo-for-07-12-acura-rdx-k23a1-2-3l-2300do-vt-t-mitsubishi-td04hl-49389",
  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>2007-2012 Acura RDX with 2.3L K23A1 2300DO-VT.T Turbocharged Engine</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>High quality replacements for factory parts; excellent quality, durability, optimizing vehicle performance</li>\n<li>OE design; simple replacement for factory part</li>\n<li>Dual valve assembly with nozzle ring inside</li>\n<li>Center rotating bearing housing designed to work with factory oil and coolant lines</li>\n<li>Component dynamically balanced using state-of-the-art balancing machine (avg 0.5 mg or less)</li>\n<li>Turbine housing made of ductile iron QT450-10; withstands temperatures up to 700°C</li>\n<li>Steel turbine wheel made from K418 alloy; high oxidation resistance, stable under temperatures up to 900°C</li>\n<li>Cast aluminum blades with good air tightness and corrosion resistance</li>\n<li>Accessories included</li>\n<li>1 year warranty for manufacturing defects</li>\n<li><em>Professional installation is highly recommended</em></li>\n<li><em>Before installation, ensure the cause of turbo failure is analyzed and eliminated (e.g., insufficient oil supply, foreign objects in intake, crankcase ventilation issues)</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Durable Compressor Wheel: 12(6+6) blades, Size: 56*42 mm</li>\n<li>Turbine Wheel: 12 blades, Size: 45.6*52 mm</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>49389-01020, 49389-01030, 49389-01031, 49189-01040</li>\n<li>49389-01041, 49389-01042, 49389-01043, 49189-08215</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>O.E.M Numbers:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>18900RWCA01, 18900-RWC-A01, 18900-RWC-A062-M3</li>\n<li>18900RWCA010M3, 18900-RWC-A010-M3</li>\n<li>18900RWCA012M3, 18900-RWC-A012-M3</li>\n<li>18900RWCA013M3, 18900-RWC-A013-M3</li>\n<li>18900RWCA014M3, 18900-RWC-A014-M3</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
